<h5 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Second place (tie, 5 mentions each):</strong></h5>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" data-attachment-id="265440" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-best-book-covers-of-the-last-decade/attachment/25937668/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/25937668.jpg" data-orig-size="818,1200" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="the bed moved" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/25937668-205x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/25937668-698x1024.jpg" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-265440" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/25937668.jpg" alt="the bed moved" width="818" height="1200" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/25937668.jpg 818w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/25937668-205x300.jpg 205w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/25937668-698x1024.jpg 698w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/25937668-768x1127.jpg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/25937668-41x60.jpg 41w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/25937668-34x50.jpg 34w" sizes="(max-width: 818px) 100vw, 818px" />Rebecca Schiff, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781101910856" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>The Bed Moved</em>,</a> cover design by <strong>Janet Hansen</strong> (Vintage, February)</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" data-attachment-id="265441" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-best-book-covers-of-the-last-decade/brit-bennett-the-mothers/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/brit-bennett-the-mothers.jpg" data-orig-size="994,1500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="brit bennett the mothers" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/brit-bennett-the-mothers-199x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/brit-bennett-the-mothers-679x1024.jpg" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-265441" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/brit-bennett-the-mothers.jpg" alt="" width="994" height="1500" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/brit-bennett-the-mothers.jpg 994w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/brit-bennett-the-mothers-199x300.jpg 199w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/brit-bennett-the-mothers-679x1024.jpg 679w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/brit-bennett-the-mothers-768x1159.jpg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/brit-bennett-the-mothers-40x60.jpg 40w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/brit-bennett-the-mothers-33x50.jpg 33w" sizes="(max-width: 994px) 100vw, 994px" />Brit Bennett, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780399184529" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>The Mothers</em></a>, cover design by <strong>Rachel Willey</strong> (Riverhead,