<h1 style="color: #b23233; text-align: center;"><strong>*</strong></h1>
<h1 style="color: #b23233; text-align: center;"><strong><a href="https://lithub.com/the-64-best-book-covers-of-2017/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2017</a>:</strong></h1>
<h5 style="text-align: center;"><strong>First place (5 mentions):</strong></h5>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="265428" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-best-book-covers-of-the-last-decade/713jhkx2bkl-_sl1500_/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/713jhkX2bKL._SL1500_.jpg" data-orig-size="992,1500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Hollow, Owen Egerton" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/713jhkX2bKL._SL1500_-198x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/713jhkX2bKL._SL1500_-677x1024.jpg" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-265428" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/713jhkX2bKL._SL1500_.jpg" alt="Hollow, Owen Egerton" width="992" height="1500" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/713jhkX2bKL._SL1500_.jpg 992w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/713jhkX2bKL._SL1500_-198x300.jpg 198w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/713jhkX2bKL._SL1500_-677x1024.jpg 677w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/713jhkX2bKL._SL1500_-768x1161.jpg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/713jhkX2bKL._SL1500_-40x60.jpg 40w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/713jhkX2bKL._SL1500_-33x50.jpg 33w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 992px) 100vw, 992px" />Owen Egerton, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781640091610" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Hollow</em></a>; cover design by <strong>Matt Dorfman</strong> (Soft Skull, July)</p>
