<h1 style="color: #b23233; text-align: center;"><strong>*</strong></h1>
<h1 style="color: #b23233; text-align: center;"><strong><a href="https://lithub.com/the-75-best-book-covers-of-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2018</a>:</strong></h1>
<h5 style="text-align: center;"><strong>First place (tie, 9 mentions each): </strong></h5>
